metadata.name: Robo-Fi NFT
metadata.description: As AI grew stronger, it was just a matter of time before these helping and useful to humans Robots start to realize how messed up the world is, so they took over the blue planet and now entering metaverse with a bang.Robo-Fi is a collection of 5,555 fully animated 3d characters created precisely on the Ethereum blockchain with a goal to build P2E game. Launched our VIP collection of 2,222 Robos now. Remaining collection of 3,333 will be a free mint for our VIP collection holders.Staking, P2E and Sci-Fi marketplace coming soon.
